111
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:31,200
After getting rid of them,

112
00:07:31,660 --> 00:07:33,280
I will succeed very soon.

113
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:34,960
Others

114
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:37,590
