308
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:47,650
You are right, my dear.

309
00:15:49,620 --> 00:15:51,750
It's Grand Tutor who worries too much.

310
00:16:02,820 --> 00:16:03,410
Report!

311
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:05,210
General Qin.

312
00:16:05,210 --> 00:16:06,470
