00:21:41,020 --> 00:21:44,580
♫I've tasted the bitterness of fate as well♫

455
00:21:44,580 --> 00:21:49,040
♫I can't hide it, yet the lonely boat can't stop sailing♫

456
00:21:55,220 --> 00:21:55,720
My Lord.

457
00:22:04,180 --> 00:22:04,600
Hurry!

