00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:10,730
I won't listen to you.

492
00:23:10,730 --> 00:23:11,930
I won't listen to you.

493
00:23:12,460 --> 00:23:13,920
I will explain everything

494
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:15,620
