00:23:26,700 --> 00:23:27,800
But you are the one who did it.

501
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:29,460
But Your Majesty acquiesced.

502
00:23:30,940 --> 00:23:31,600
Also,

503
00:23:32,740 --> 00:23:33,740
don't forget that

504
00:23:34,700 --> 00:23:36,360
