506
00:23:38,820 --> 00:23:40,680
You faked the late emperor's will

507
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:43,560
and forced him to fight a suicide battle.

508
00:23:45,620 --> 00:23:46,420
Your Majesty.

509
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:49,930
There's no turning back.

510
00:23:56,900 --> 00:23:58,000
I guess

511
00:23:58,580 --> 00:23:59,410
I don't have to

512
00:24:00,020 --> 00:24:01,300
