523
00:24:51,700 --> 00:24:53,360
Are you leading the officials

524
00:24:53,580 --> 00:24:54,780
to press His Majesty?

525
00:24:57,820 --> 00:24:58,620
Your Majesty.

526
00:25:00,700 --> 00:25:01,770
General Zhou

527
00:25:02,220 --> 00:25:04,380
